From the manufacturer

The Concept

Be seduced by the essence of mystery GUESS Seductive Blue for Men. A mysterious and intriguing scent that embodies the unique magnetism and playfully captivating style synonymous with the GUESS brand.

The Scent

Infused with refreshing notes of black pepper, geranium, and cashmere wood, the fragrance evokes the essence of the iconic fashion brand and is a new interpretation of modern masculinity.

Fragrance Family: Oriental Woody

Key Notes:

  • Top Notes: Caviar, Cardamom, Black Pepper
  • Middle Notes: Blue Coral, Aqua Space, Geranium
  • Base Notes: Cashmere Wood, Moss, Rippled Sand

How customer reviews and ratings work

Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we dont use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.

About this Item

  • Fragrance Story: GUESS Seductive Blue, is a powerful scent that embodies the unique magnetism and playfully captivating style synonymous with the GUESS brand. Infused with refreshing notes of black pepper, Geranium and Cashmere wood. The oriental fragrance evokes the essence of the iconic fashion brand, channeling the edgy, trendsetting designs that have set GUESS apart throughout its history.
  • Olfactive Family: Oriental Woody
  • Fragrance Notes: Top - Caviar, Cardamom, Black Pepper / Mid - Blue Coral, AquaSpace, Geranium / Base - Cashmere Wood, Moss, Rippled Sand
